VERSION 6.6.2 (May 13, 2011) LINUXTAG RELEASE --------------------------

  API:
  [ADD] JAX-RX API now supports basic user authentication:
        http://docs.basex.org/wiki/JAX-RX_API
  [ADD] The COPY creates identical database copies:
